Package com.bws.jdistil.core.tag.action

Class Summary
ActionComponent Abstract base component containing attributes common to all action UI components.
ActionData Action data component used in the bodies of tags descending from ActionComponent to specify form field data to populate before submitting the form.
BreadcrumbAction Breadcrumb action component used in the bodies of BreadcrumbTrail tags to specify action IDs to be tracked by the breadcrumb trail.
BreadcrumbTrail Component used to display a trail of breadcrumb links.
Button Button component used to perform some action.
Link Link component used to perform some action.
Menu Menu component used to display a menu and its associated as menu items.
MenuBar Menu bar component used to display one or more menus and their associated menu items.
MenuItem Menu items component used to display content as menu items.
PopupMenu Popup menu component used to display content as menu items invoked by a button.
PopupMenuItem Popup menu items component used to display content as menu items.
